  • Method Details

    • getJsonObjectFromApi

      public com.google.gson.JsonObject getJsonObjectFromApi​(String urlString)
      This method implements the iAPI interface and returns the JSON data from a given URL as JsonObject. Used to get information about the DegreePrograms, StudyModules and Courses from the Sisu API.
      Specified by:
      getJsonObjectFromApi in interface iAPI
      Parameters:
      urlString - The URL of the page we wish to get JSON data from.
      Returns:
      JsonObject json.

    • parseDegreePrograms

      public TreeSet<DegreeProgram> parseDegreePrograms() throws MalformedURLException
      This method goes through all of the DegreePrograms in the Sisu API, adds them to a TreeSet and returns them to the GUI-class Sisu.java.
      Returns:
      degreePrograms
      Throws:
      MalformedURLException

    • parseModules

      public DegreeProgram parseModules​(DegreeProgram dp) throws MalformedURLException
      This function takes in the DegreeProgram given by the user and adds StudyModules and Courses to it recursively from the Sisu API, before returning the populated DegreeProgram.
      Parameters:
      dp - DegreeProgram that the user chooses from the GUI
      Returns:
      DegreeProgram populated with StudyModules populated with Courses.
      Throws:
      MalformedURLException

    • recursionOverRulesDP

      public void recursionOverRulesDP​(com.google.gson.JsonObject rule)
      This is the main recursion function, which calls other sub-recursive functions depending of the type of the given rule.
      Parameters:
      rule - The rule JsonObject

    • recursionCompositeRule

      public void recursionCompositeRule​(com.google.gson.JsonObject rule)
      This method does the recursion over type CompositeRule. CompositeRule contains rules as subrules.
      Parameters:
      rule - Given rule as JsonObject for the recursion

    • recursionModuleRule

      public void recursionModuleRule​(com.google.gson.JsonObject rule)
      This method does the recursion over type ModuleRule. These are the StudyModules added to the DegreeProgram. A messy if else structure is implemented due to inconsistencies in the Sisu API.
      Parameters:
      rule - Given rule as JsonObject for the recursion

    • recursionCreditsRule

      public void recursionCreditsRule​(com.google.gson.JsonObject rule)
      This method does the recursion over type CreditsRule. We continue past it since it does not contain interesting data.
      Parameters:
      rule - Given rule as JsonObject for the recursion.

    • recursionCourseUnitRule

      public void recursionCourseUnitRule​(com.google.gson.JsonObject rule)
      This method does the recursion over type CourseUnitRule, creates Courses from the data and adds them to the current StudyModule. Messy if else structure implemented also here due to the features of the Sisu API. Recursion ends here.
      Parameters:
      rule - Given rule as JsonObject for the recursion
